          About Susan Cain
        

          Susan Cain is the co-founder of Quiet Revolution and the author of the bestseller Quiet Power: The Secret Strengths of Introverts, and Quiet: The Power of Introverts in A World That Can't Stop Talking. I'm also the co-founder of the Quiet Schools Network and the Quiet Leadership Institute. 
        







